===政府監控===
2018年8月，Telegram修改隱私政策，如果執法調查單位能夠證明特定用戶的身份為恐怖分子，將配合法院要求提供該用戶的IP、電話號碼等資料。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125600|title=Telegram更新隱私政策，必要時將交出用戶資料給政府|author=林妍溱|date=2018-08-30|publisher=電週文化事業|access-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019121927/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125600|archive-date=2018-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://telegram.org/privacy|title=Telegram Privacy Policy|quote=8.3. Law Enforcement Authorities: If Telegram receives a court order that confirms you're a terror suspect, we may disclose your IP address and phone number to the relevant authorities.|date=2018-08-14|publisher=Telegram|access-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908095619/https://telegram.org/privacy|archive-date=2015-09-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

